imdb.plot outline: Celebrities tell us their own story in their own words. Unscripted, up close and personal, and told in a compelling, dynamic, entertaining, thought-provoking manner, so that their life story connects with the viewer. These icons of stage, screen, politics, music and literature share with us their passion, vision, hope, belief, loss and triumph.
imdb.title: Unscripted
plot: Celebrities tell us their own story in their own words. _Unscripted_ (qv), up close and personal, and told in a compelling, dynamic, entertaining, thought-provoking manner, so that their life story connects with the viewer.
